has been worked out" but the "mechanisms and the principles for
putting it into practice" pose the major obstacles, he said.
</P>
<P>
He again urged NATO to halt its air raids on Yugoslavia, which
entered the 69th day Monday.
</P>
<P>
"The West must understand what might happen if this concrete
decision is not made" at the trilateral talks, he said. 
