<HEADLINE> New Bahraini Cabinet Sworn in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIYADH, May 31 (Xinhua) -- The new Bahraini cabinet was sworn
in before Emir Sheikh Hamad Bin Isa al-Khalifa on Monday,
according to media reports reaching here.
</P>
<P>
