public freedom and serve the interests of the people.
</P>
<P>
Most of the former ministers maintained their posts in the new
cabinet, the first which was formed since Sheikh Hamad came to
power after his father died of a heart attack last March.
</P>
<P>
There are only three new faces in the new cabinet, those of the
ministers of electricity, finance and national economy, commerce
and agriculture. 
