Piturca has to face tough team problems. Midfielder Ioan Ovidiu
Sabau was given up for medical reasons, Piturca is compelled to
wait for the GP's verdict, Adrian Ilie was suffering from a right
leg strain, and Dan Petrescu underwent surgery with amygdalitis
last Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
For injured goalkeeper Bogdan Stelea, the Romanian national
squad's physician said the prospect for his showing on Saturday is
but 50 percent.
</P>
<P>
Romanian soccer fans have showed great interest in the Romania-
Hungary match as they queued up for hours on Moday when the
tickets were put on sale.
</P>
<P>
As tickets supply was far below demand, the price of a ticket
on the black market surged up to 100 DM, and was still expected to
grow as the match's day approached.
</P>
