across the country for International Children's Day.
</P>
<P>
In the nation's capital, more than 20,000 children from
different countries had a grand get-together at the Children's
Palace for art performances and games. One 12 year-old Yugoslav
boy called it a very happy day and said that he hoped his friends
back home could also have a joyful festival.
</P>
