<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, June 1 (Xinhua) -- Six people were killed and 11 others
seriously injured as a wayward six-wheeled dump truck fell into a
deep ravine in the Cebu City in central Philippines on Tuesday
morning, a police report reaching here said.
</P>
<P>
