<HEADLINE> Francesco Flores to Swear in as El Salvador's 34th President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, May 31 (Xinhua)-- Francisco Flores will swear in
Tuesday as President of El Salvador for the next five years after
his electoral victory on March 7.
</P>
<P>
Flores, 39, economist, will become the 34th president of this
Central American country.
</P>
